---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">When Should You Upgrade Your PC vs Buy New in 2026?</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-gray-200">
                <p>Not sure whether to upgrade your current computer or buy a new one? Here's a practical guide to help you decide based on your needs and budget.</p>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Upgrade If...</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-6">
                        <li>Your CPU is relatively recent (Intel 8th gen or Ryzen 2000 series or newer)</li>
                        <li>You're still using a traditional hard drive instead of an SSD</li>
                        <li>You have at least 8GB of RAM and room to add more</li>
                        <li>You mainly need better graphics (just add a new GPU + power supply)</li>
                        <li>You have a limited budget (under $300–400)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Buy New If...</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-6">
                        <li>Your system is from 2018 or older</li>
                        <li>You want modern features (Wi-Fi 7, DDR5 memory, newer CPU architecture, etc.)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Let Us Help</h2>
                    <p>RigRescue offers honest, unbiased advice on part selection, full build services, or remote diagnostics to help you make the smartest choice for your budget and needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-16">
                <a href="/contact"
                   class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Personalized PC Advice
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
